                 full           Citycalls without a "0" at the beginning are allowed
                 
                 national       Calls with ONE "0" at the beginning are allowed

                 international  All calls are allowed

 @{fg shine}rating-factor@{fg text}   Define a factor which is multiplied ba the rating.


